Reasoning: 
- cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing): The title and abstract explicitly mention distributed computing, which is the main focus of this sub-category.
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms): The paper discusses the cost of accessing and storing data, which is related to data structures and algorithms.
- cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture): The paper discusses the cost of network traffic and bandwidth, which is related to networking and internet architecture.
- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper discusses how to structure distributed computing systems to optimize cost, which is related to systems and control.
- cs.SE (Software Engineering): The paper may be of interest to software engineers who are designing and implementing distributed computing systems.
